---
import Container from '../components/Container.astro';
import FadeUp from '../components/FadeUp';
---

<section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-pure-cream">
  <Container>
    <FadeUp client:visible>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="inline-block text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xinjiang-red mb-3">The Specialty</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold text-charred-brown leading-tight">
          Lamb, noodles, chili oil.<br />The holy trinity.
        </h2>
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-earth-brown leading-relaxed text-left sm:text-center">
          <p>
            The roast lamb ribs are deep-fried until crispy, then tossed in cumin, chili, and Sichuan peppercorns. They disappear in minutes. Half our reviews are about this one dish.
          </p>
          <p>
            The hand-pulled noodles are made fresh — stretched by hand into thin strands, served in a rich lamb broth. The dumplings come swimming in smoky aromatic chili oil that's been described as "addictive."
          </p>
          <p>
            This isn't fusion. This isn't modern interpretation. This is how Chinese Muslims in Xinjiang have been eating for generations. We just brought it to KL.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </FadeUp>
  </Container>
</section>
